(b)  the  disclosure  is  made  in  circumstances  where  the 
information  provided  is  framed  in  such  a  manner  that 
the  source  of  the  information  could  not  be  ascertained;

(d)  the  disclosure  is  made  to  facilitate  the  performance  of 
the  functions  of  the  Controller,  Deputy  Controller  or 
Assistant  Controller;

